name: create_graph_model
query:
CREATE (:Music {name: "Guitar", type: "String"})<-[:PLAYS]-(:Person {name: "Thomas", location: "Montpellier"})-[:STUDIES_IN {since: 2022}]->(n2:University {name: "UM", departement: "Polytech"})<-[:STUDIES_IN {since: 2022}]-(n0:Person {name: "Sylvain", location: "Montpellier"})-[:WORKS_OUT {since: 2023}]->(:Gym {name: "BoulderLine", location: "Montpellier"}),
(n2)<-[:STUDIES_IN {since: 2022}]-(:Person {name: "Charley", location: "Montpellier"})-[:PRACTICES]->(:Sport {name: "climbing", type: "individual"})<-[:PRACTICES]-(n0)-[:LIKES]->(:Beer {name: "Cherry Chouffe", alcohol_level: 8})

name: get_person_and_beer_relationship
query:
MATCH (n: Person)-[r: LIKES]->(b: Beer)
RETURN n, r, b

name: get_person_and_sport_relationship
query:
MATCH (n: Person)-[r: PRACTICES]->(b: Sport)
RETURN n, r, b

name: get_person_and_sport_relationship_conditional
query:
MATCH (n: Person)-[r: PRACTICES]->(b: Sport)
WHERE n.name = "Sylvain"
RETURN n, r, b
